@NODE info "MUI XAnim - English manual"
@{B}*** Why did I write MUI XAnim ? ***@{UB}

MUI XAnim is a Graphic User Interface to use with the program 
XAnim (© Mark Podlipec).

I decided to write this GUI for easier use because  XAnim was a 
shell only program and with this quantity of options it is not very
easy to use.

So I Hope it will be helpfull for those who hate using shell.

Note that all available XAnim options aren't implemented in MUIXAnim, I only
selected the most usefull for me.
If you think I should include more options or add something to MUI XAnim,
please @{"contact me" link adress}.

The @{B}UNREGISTERED@{UB} Demo version has the following limitations :
@{fg shine}You cannot save your preferences.@{fg text}
That's the only limitation, but if you like this program, please @{"register" link adress}
so I will do other interfaces.

You have a 30 days free period to test it.

@ENDNODE


